{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_14_level_spst_14-01","storyGroup":"main_14","storySort":210,"storyDependence":"main_14_level_spst_14-01","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"EG-6","storyName":"慈悲遗愿","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"过去与未来，特蕾西娅在源石的信息之海中瞥见了生命的答案。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_spst_14-01","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"spst_14-01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":39,"characters":["弗莱蒙特","艾尔启","埃克提尔尼尔","娜斯提","克丽斯腾","“保存者”","歌蕾蒂娅","凯尔希","伊万杰利斯塔十一世","教宗骑士"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/dd/Avg_bg_bg_light.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":5},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_desolate_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"text","text":"这是一场永远不会终结的远行。","id":10},{"type":"text","text":"众魂的言语早已沉寂，身影也几乎在长久的磋磨中失去了形状。","id":11},{"type":"text","text":"唯有他们的魔王，仍在替所有人前行。","id":12},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅不愿停下脚步。","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"过去她也曾数度走向“魔王”深处。可这次与以前任何一次漫步都有所不同。她不再为那些浩瀚的知识驻足。","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"她只是在看。","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"最后一次，用她自己的眼睛，看向那些大地上的人与事——","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"发生的，或者尚未发生的。","id":17},{"type":"dialog","id":18},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"charslot","id":21},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_bg_44_g4_towerroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":22},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#3$1","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":24},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":26},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"......她最终还是走到了这一步。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"该说我们的殿下什么好呢？冥顽不灵，还是天赋异禀？算了，不管骂还是夸，这下连众魂都听不见了。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"维多利亚的事情暂时放一边吧。那边的烂摊子特雷西斯和孽茨雷会收拾的。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"接下来......哈，瓦瑟领的高塔上塞满了军事委员会的间谍。他们恨不得撺掇羊和猫立刻大干一架，好让他们别关注卡兹戴尔。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"把你们的线都收收好！记住，我们也很快就要滚蛋了。浮夸羊不会容忍我们继续在她眼皮子底下蹦跶。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"我早就跟菈玛莲抱怨过，那对兄妹太激进了，迟早会给我们招来数不清的麻烦事！","id":34,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"埃芒加德，你在卡兹戴尔的活儿得加紧做了。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"要是特雷西斯的计划没完全成功，维多利亚......不，莱塔尼亚和其他核心圈国家的军队会立刻朝卡兹戴尔行进。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"接收巴别塔留下的遗产，保住那座城市。不能让两百年前的事再来一次。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"......等等。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"线头是不是动了？埃芒加德，是你动的吗？","id":40,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a1/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"......","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b7/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"这样啊。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b7/Avg_avg_npc_1114_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":44},{"type":"multiline","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"“希望”......我可不怎么喜欢听见这个词语。但好歹，眼前还算有条路可以走......","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1114_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":46},{"type":"multiline","name":"弗莱蒙特","text":"对吧，殿下？","id":47},{"type":"dialog","id":48},{"type":"charslot","id":49},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅看到老巫妖严肃的脸上露出了一个几不可见的微笑。","id":50},{"type":"text","text":"她松开了那根透明的、深入虚空的丝弦，朝那位暂停了抱怨的老朋友点了点头，又朝更远的地方走去。","id":51},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"charslot","id":55},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bf/Avg_bg_40_g2_glacier.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#1$3","id":57},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#10$1","id":58},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":59},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":60},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":61},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#1$3","focus":"l","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"......","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-1$3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#8$3","focus":"l","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"我看见，那处影子有了变化。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-8$3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"又是噩兆？","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#8$3","focus":"l","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"......不全是。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-8$3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"你来寻我，将远见的结果告知，我很感激。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"但我心意已决。邪魔带来的污染正在蔓延，如果我们一而再再而三地往南退，萨米的沦陷将是迟早的事。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#1$3","focus":"l","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"即便，我见到的关于你的所有未来......皆是悲剧？","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f3/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-1$3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"我知道。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"早在我成为雪祀......不，在我降生于这片冰原，成长为一名萨米战士起，我就知晓了自己的结局。","id":77,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"我并不畏惧死亡。我也并不忧虑邪魔夺取我的躯壳，令我转化为播撒污秽的敌人。","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"会有更年轻的战士循着我的足印，走向更北的北方。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"若不幸与被转化的我相遇，他们会用弓和法杖清除我残躯上的污浊。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"既然守护萨米的意志不会轻易死去，我便不会视这样的结果为“悲剧”。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"那么......祝福你，远征之人。","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"请拿着这个吧。","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"密文板？","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"临别赠礼。","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"我听说，多数独眼巨人已做出离开萨米诸部族的决定。而你则选择了留下。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"有一则预言......关于这片土地上的生机，我必须令它实现。","id":93,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/bd/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_968_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"萨卡兹，萨米会感谢你这么多年来的付出。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"埃克提尔尼尔","text":"你对我分享了你的远见，我也赠予你我听到的声音。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1e/Avg_avg_npc_968_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_969_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾尔启","text":"嗯......","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2a/Avg_avg_npc_969_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":99},{"type":"charslot","id":100},{"type":"text","text":"号角声响彻冰原。","id":101},{"type":"text","text":"这是远征的信号，亦是悠远的致意。","id":102},{"type":"text","text":"眼前的独眼巨人或许不会再回到卡兹戴尔，这片冰封之地已然是她的家园。","id":103},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅的视线与艾尔启的视线重叠。","id":104},{"type":"text","text":"她在雪祀留下的木板上看见了奇妙的纹路。","id":105},{"type":"text","text":"“埃克纶”。","id":106},{"type":"text","text":"草木兽羽有枯荣......","id":107},{"type":"text","text":"祈愿久延存。","id":108},{"type":"dialog","id":109},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":110},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":111},{"type":"charslot","id":112},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_bg_27_g26_dusk_wild.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_891_1#1$1","id":114},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":115},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_891_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"......找到了。","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"这个读数......一定就在附近。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":121},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_footstep_stonestep","volume":"0.6","channel":"step1","loop":"false","id":122},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"step1","fadetime":"2","id":123},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_537_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":124},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":125},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_891_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"小心。我的计算不可能出错，所以，我们目前就踩在哥伦比亚......不，所有现代国家最伟大的考古发现正上方。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_537_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"那立刻穿一个洞，将导能电缆和我一起送到下面去，如何？","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_891_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"马里亚姆不会高兴的。他一定更希望我们小心地探索和发掘。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_891_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"不过，谁让他一直待在北地不回来呢？负责干这活的是工程科。","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"在通知你之前，我的人已经开工了。","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_537_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"很好。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"介意我做第一个下去的人吗？","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":138},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_891_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":139},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_originiumcastshort","volume":"0.6","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"（萨卡兹语）“卫护”。","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/17/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"嗯？你很少在工作场合使用咒术。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_891_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"首先我得确保面前的人不会被这些萨卡兹的小把戏吓垮。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"总辖女士，我本该再念几句安全须知，但你也不会有心思听的。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"娜斯提","text":"军队和梅兰德的人马上就要找过来了。无论你希望找到什么——都必须抓紧了。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5f/Avg_avg_npc_891_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_537_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"我会的。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/27/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_537_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克丽斯腾","text":"在死亡的阴翳蒙上我的双眼之前......我会尽力去看我想看见的一切。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_537_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"charslot","id":156},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8d/Avg_bg_38_g8_storage.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":158},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":160},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅看见了。","id":161},{"type":"text","text":"时间又前进了些。她能感到这个地方在拒斥着她。","id":162},{"type":"text","text":"她想起多年前，自己跟着凯尔希，第一次靠近罗德岛本舰的最深处。","id":163},{"type":"text","text":"这个相似的地方，是她从未踏足之地，一片......属于“神明”的居所。","id":164},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_energybody","volume":"1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"（未知语言）那个可爱的小家伙才刚刚离开......又有新的闯入者。","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"（未知语言）嗯......没有吗？","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"（未知语言）在你带来的这些小小的数据涟漪中，我感受到了一丝熟悉。","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"（未知语言）或许你和我一样，都是被留在过去，不得已在不属于自己的时代苟延残喘的......幽灵。","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"（未知语言）是什么支撑着你跋涉至此......一个同样微弱且渺茫的希望吗？","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“保存者”","text":"（未知语言）还是对无法再见的同类的怀念？","id":171},{"type":"dialog","id":172},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"charslot","id":175},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/eb/Avg_bg_27_g24_cloudy_sea.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":176},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":177},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":179},{"type":"dialog","id":180},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_spear","volume":"1","id":181},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_imp_gunlance_n","volume":"1","delay":"0.2","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":183},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","duration":"0.7","id":184},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","duration":"0.7","id":185},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":186},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"医生，小心我的槊，它可能会划伤您那脆弱的皮肤。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"无妨。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"海面之下暂时没有值得您注意的东西。您在凝望的，究竟是什么？","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"一些回忆罢了。","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我曾认为阿戈尔远离大地，面临的是另一种问题。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可或许......我并不完全正确。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","focus":"l","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"您竟然在这个时候反省。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我只是不希望自己又一次到得太迟。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"假如海洋的问题并不独立，那我们所面临的威胁将会叠加到一起。这比任何已知推演中的绝境还要棘手。","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"好在，我们有机会在危机被引爆之前，先一步抓住主动权。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#3","focus":"l","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"但愿等您随我一同回到阿戈尔，您依然能保持同等程度的自信。","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"歌蕾蒂娅，我相信的是猎人们。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#4","focus":"l","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......有趣的说辞。","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_4.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"深海猎人从海底来到陆上，又即将回到故乡。我看着你们一路的变化。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#4","focus":"l","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"变化......呵呵，这可未必是我期望的。","id":213,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_4.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你们会在来处找到自己。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"无论是你，还是斯卡蒂和幽灵鲨，抑或你们那位选择独自离去的同伴。","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","focus":"l","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......乌尔比安。","id":218,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"做好准备吧。","id":220,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"到那时，你们会对阿戈尔......对海洋与陆地，对“我们”需要共同面对的浩劫，产生不同的看法。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这远比任何肉眼可见的“桥梁”有价值。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":223},{"type":"charslot","id":224},{"type":"text","text":"星星点点的光粒浮起，在海面上投下了清晰的影子。","id":225},{"type":"text","text":"就像凯尔希说的，宛如“桥梁”。","id":226},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅踏上那座虚空中的桥。时间和浪花一起加速，她很难再掌控自己意识的行进。","id":227},{"type":"text","text":"凯尔希......凯尔希。","id":228},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅努力地回头凝望着好友，以及好友身后的新朋友和老朋友——","id":229},{"type":"text","text":"直到他们和小小的光粒融为一体。","id":230},{"type":"dialog","id":231},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"charslot","id":234},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_bg_26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":236},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":238},{"type":"text","text":"光粒在扩大。","id":239},{"type":"text","text":"曾经的魔王发现自己正站在一座教堂中央，沐浴着最为圣洁的辉光。","id":240},{"type":"text","text":"而头顶光环的萨科塔教宗，正与她“对视”着。","id":241},{"type":"text","text":"于河畔偶遇的年轻信使，教堂窗前的平和老者......她记得他，岁月亦无法干扰她的判断。","id":242},{"type":"dialog","id":243},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":244},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_356_1#8$1","duration":"1","id":245},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":246},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_356_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"......很久没有新的名字出现了。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"这算不算好事？","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"短短几年间，我们可多了不少“圣徒”。那里面的好几位，我都有些......难以苟同。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我们至今仍未知晓，圣徒们各自会在未来扮演什么角色。","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/68/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"教宗阁下，既然不再有新的圣徒被选中，是不是意味着......危机有可能已经解除了？","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"你很乐观。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我也希望，我们的拉特兰，能长久地保持这种乐观。","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"然而......","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_356_1#8$1","focus":"r","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"......","id":261,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"过去，它从未缄口不言。","id":262,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_356_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_358_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"呃——！","id":264,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"阁下，有一瞬间，我感觉不到——","id":265,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗骑士","text":"不，这怎么可能？！","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9c/Avg_avg_npc_358_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":267},{"type":"charslot","id":268},{"type":"text","text":"光熄灭了。","id":269},{"type":"text","text":"先是一盏灯，然后是一片街区。","id":270},{"type":"text","text":"从启示石塔到米迦莱昂区的公证所，再到圣马尔索区的夕辉礼拜堂，教堂广场——","id":271},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":273},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":274},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"charslot","id":276},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":277},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":278},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":279},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_reawakeningpiano_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":280,"musicid":1},{"type":"text","text":"黑暗在前进。","id":281},{"type":"text","text":"迅速，无序，不可抵挡。","id":282},{"type":"text","text":"冰原，海洋，陆地。","id":283},{"type":"text","text":"所有的讯号都预示着未来人们将遭遇的磨难，就和她无数次通过“魔王”看到的一样。","id":284},{"type":"dialog","id":285},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":287},{"type":"charslot","id":288},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8f/Avg_bg_49_g12_sandstorm.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":290},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_sandwnd","volume":"0","loop":"true","channel":"wind","id":291},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","fadetime":"3","channel":"wind","id":292},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":294},{"type":"text","text":"她走出黑暗时，脚下却已是松软的黄沙。","id":295},{"type":"text","text":"废墟，晶簇，沙丘......眼前的一切她如此陌生。","id":296},{"type":"text","text":"扬起沙尘的狂风中，她听到了，看到了，感受到了那位孤独的少女。","id":297},{"type":"text","text":"那个迎面走来，笼罩在斗篷中的身影，撩起帽檐。","id":298},{"type":"text","text":"源石在少女的脚下如雪痕般绽放，特蕾西娅看到了少女眼中的菱形瞳孔——","id":299},{"type":"text","text":"你是......","id":300},{"type":"dialog","id":301},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":302},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":303},{"type":"charslot","id":304},{"type":"curtain","id":305},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":306},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":307},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":308},{"type":"text","text":"黄沙漫过，她的双眼已被遮蔽。","id":309},{"type":"dialog","id":310},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"wind","fadetime":"2","id":311},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":312},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":313},{"type":"charslot","id":314},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_5_7_shining.png","fadetime":"0","screenadapt":"coverall","id":315},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":316},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":317},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":318},{"type":"text","text":"这并非终点，但已是特蕾西娅能够触及的最远处。","id":319},{"type":"text","text":"黑暗正朝她挤压过来，即将封堵她的去路，捂住她的眼睛、她的思想。","id":320},{"type":"text","text":"唯有她热烈的情感，仍在这片永恒的幽暗中荡漾。","id":321},{"type":"text","text":"她曾带着千万个问题一路跋涉，走到自我的尽头，却只渴求着一个最为简单的回答。","id":322},{"type":"dialog","id":323},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"4","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/89/Avg_50_i34.png","fadetime":"0","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"bgeffect","name":"$eb_tlxy_laugh","layer":"1","id":326},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":327},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"5","block":"true","id":328},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":329},{"type":"dialog","id":330},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":331},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":332},{"type":"sticker","id":333,"text":"“在这些未来，以及更遥远的未来之中......","x":"300","y":"300","alignment":"center","size":"28","delay":"0","duration":"2.5","width":"700"},{"type":"sticker","id":334,"text":"“还有我爱的人们的影子吗？”","x":"300","y":"380","alignment":"center","size":"28","delay":"0","duration":"2.5","width":"700"},{"type":"sticker","id":335,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"sticker","id":336,"duration":"1","block":"false"},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":337},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":338},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":339},{"type":"text","text":"特蕾西娅迫切地寻找着，看向那黑暗之中唯一的光明处——","id":340},{"type":"text","text":"她得到了答案。","id":341},{"type":"dialog","id":342},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"6","block":"true","id":343},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":344},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":345},{"type":"bgeffect","id":346},{"type":"charslot","id":347},{"type":"image","id":348}],"characters":["弗莱蒙特","艾尔启","埃克提尔尼尔","娜斯提","克丽斯腾","“保存者”","歌蕾蒂娅","凯尔希","伊万杰利斯塔十一世","教宗骑士"]}